videos.description: Oklahoma's Isaiah Cousins goes in for the big-time slam but Washington State's Valentine Izundu will have none of it, making the monster block that starts the fast break on the other end.
videos.headline: Don't come hard to the rim when Izundu is around

videos.description: In the final seconds of the half, Oklahoma's Dante Buford grabs the miss and slams it home for the emphatic dunk that gets the seal of approval from ESPN's Brad Daugherty.
videos.headline: Putback dunk has Brad Daugherty all kinds of excited

videos.description: While it will go down as a made field goal, Oklahoma's Khadeem Lattin had no intention of making a basket via wild deflection but will still take the two points.
videos.headline: Better to be lucky than good, but two points is two points
